The '''Eulogio "Amang" Rodriguez Institute of Science and Technology''' is a State College which provides quality higher learning in the areas of science and technology.
Ing '''Eulogio "Amang" Rodriguez Institute of Science and Technology''' metung yang colegiung pang-estadung babye matas a uring pamagaral king ciencia at tecnologia.




== Amlat ==
Ing Pamuntuk ning Senadu, i [[w:Eulogio Rodriquez|Eulogio Rodriguez]], ing mitatag king EARIST kaybat ning [[w:World War II|guerra]].  Antimong metung a meging alcaldi ning [[Menila]], penamdaman nang kaylangan de reng tau Menila ing metung a pipagaralan a munye pamagsaneng vocational at trade.  Migumpisa ya ing EARIST antimong departamentung vocational ning V. Mapa High School.
